Refactor:
----------
1. While creating anything in kubernetes, check if it is already there or not.

NOTE: 
    - Only one port can be mapped to one container port.
    - Eg: 2222 and 2223 cannot be mapped to 22.
    - So 2222:22 and 2223:23 should be done. 2222:22 and 2223:22 is not supported.
